 '布里奇特·琼斯（Bridget Jones）：对男孩的导演疯狂https://www.nme.com/news/film/film/bridget-jones-mad-about-the-boy-defends-previous-films-films-over-accusations-of-misogyny-3838244？ Bridget-Jones-Mad-Abod-boy-Dilector-Defends-defious-Films-over-of-MisodynyChris Edwards Fri, 14 Feb 2025 20:03:13 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3838244 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这是一个非常不同的时间”</p><p>帖子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/bridget-jones-mad-about-the-boy-director-defends-previous-films-over-accusations-of-misogyny-3838244">“布里奇特·琼斯（Bridget Jones）：对男孩导演的疯狂”捍卫了以前的电影，因为厌女症的指控</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Bridget-Jones-Mad-About-the-Boy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/20